data.description: Absolutely stunning 3 bed+loft townhome in amazing location near all the great restaurants & shopping that Arcadia has to offer. Perfect opportunity to own in this highly sought after gated community. Walk into the immaculate home- Modern kitchen with ample storage, ss appliances, quartz countertops, walk-in pantry,custom tile, woodwork and more. Custom mud room area from your direct access 2 car garage. Upstairs loft offers cozy separate area to relax, create your home office or make it a playroom for the kids. Oversized main bedroom w/ custom barn door into ensuite bath w/ large walk-in shower. Huge custom master suite walk in closetLaundry room equipped with W/D stays w/ the home. Backyard sanctuary with turf and covered patio, perfect spot for morning coffee. Time to plant roots HERE!
